I have a research position at CONICET.
My main research areas are the logic
of science (especially within
metatheoretical structuralism) and
the philosophy of biology (especially
of systematics).I have published more
than 20 articles, book chapters,
reviews, theses, etc. To know more,
exit through the door to your right.
